[title size="2"]Avada Has Unlimited Color Options![/title]
Avada includes a backend color picker in the theme options that allows you to easily change the color throughout the entire theme. Simply select the color picker and pick a new color, or insert a hex or rgb number and the new color value will be implemented throughout the entire site. We put time and effort into building Avada, making sure that all buttons, bullets, links, text, roll overs and other items were created with CSS3 so they could be manipulated by the color picker. The beautifully made CSS3 buttons with gradients and roll overs can easily be changed to any color you desire. Enjoy!";s:10:"post_title";s:16:"Unlimited Colors";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:23:"superb-customer-support";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-07-31 04:48:43";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-07-31 04:48:43";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:80;s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://theme-fusion.com/avada/?page_id=132";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}